Method.СообщитьПользователю.Description=Generates and outputs a message that may be associated with a form control.\nIn a long operation background job, if the call is performed outside of a transaction,\nthe message is written to a service register and sent to the client immediately,\nif the interaction system is connected.\nAt the end of a long operation background job, as well as when sending progress,\nall messages are extracted from the background job message queue,\nwritten to a service register and sent to the client immediately,\nif the interaction system is connected.
Method.СообщитьПользователю.Example.Description=1. To output a message at a managed form field associated with an object attribute\:\nCommon.NotifyUser(\nNStr("en \= 'Error message.'"), ,\n"FieldInObjectFormAttribute",\n"Object");\nAlternative usage in an object form\:\nCommon.NotifyUser(\nNStr("en \= 'Error message.'"), ,\n"Object.FieldInObjectFormAttribute");\n2. To output a message next to a managed form field associated with a form attribute\:\nCommon.NotifyUser(\nNStr("en \= 'Error message.'"), ,\n"FormAttributeName");\n3. To output a message associated with an information base object\:\nCommon.NotifyUser(\nNStr("en \= 'Error message.'"), InformationBaseObject, "Responsible",,Cancel);\n4. To output a message by reference to an information base object\:\nCommon.NotifyUser(\nNStr("en \= 'Error message.'"), Reference, , , Cancel);\nCases of incorrect usage\:\n1. Passing both DataKey and DataPath parameters at the same time.\n2. Passing a value of a type other than allowed in the DataKey parameter.\n3. Setting a reference without setting a field (and/or path to data).
Method.СообщитьПользователю.Name=NotifyUser
Method.СообщитьПользователю.Param.КлючДанных.Description=object, reference, or record key of the information base to which this message refers.
Method.СообщитьПользователю.Param.КлючДанных.Name=DataKey
