Method.ХранилищеНастроекДанныхФормЗагрузить.Description=Loads a setting from the form data settings storage, like the platform Load method,\nof the StandardSettingsStorageManager or SettingsStorageManager.<Storage name> objects,\nbut with support for setting key length over 128 characters by hashing the part\nthat exceeds 96 characters.\nIn addition, returns the specified default value if the settings are not found.\nIf there is no SaveUserData right, the default value is returned without error.\nIn the returned value, references to non-existent objects in the database are cleared, namely\n- the returned reference is replaced with the specified default value;\n- references are removed from data of type Array;\n- in data of type Structure and Map, the key does not change, and the value is set to Undefined;\n- analysis of values in data of type Array, Structure, Map is performed recursively.
Method.ХранилищеНастроекДанныхФормЗагрузить.Name=FormDataSettingsStorageLoad
Method.ХранилищеНастроекДанныхФормЗагрузить.Param.ЗначениеПоУмолчанию.Description=value that is returned if the settings are not found.\nIf not specified, Undefined is returned.
